 criminal profiling, must hunt down the ritual murderer who has been terrorizing the city for two decades.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0835,"vote_count":339,"poster_path":"/xOA4MbyJZVJHGZ38wC4LPpruBBX.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-25","vote_average":5.627,"backdrop_path":"/tr0QbJHWjI3pWhY75oTNl3o9lcC.jpg","original_title":"El silencio de la ciudad blanca","original_language":"es"},{"id":576017,"adult":false,"title":"For Sama","video":false,"overview":"A love letter from a young mother to her daughter, the film tells the story of Waad al-Kateab’s life through five years of the uprising in Aleppo, Syria as she falls in love, gets married and gives birth to Sama, all while cataclysmic conflict rises around her.  Her camera captures incredible stories of loss, laughter and survival as Waad wrestles with an impossible choice– whether or not to flee the city to protect her daughter’s life, when leaving means abandoning the struggle for freedom for which she has already sacrificed so much.","genre_ids":[99,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9412,"vote_count":302,"poster_path":"/mDna51F8QfrJFZOgPGQUz3VKqsB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-26","vote_average":8.219,"backdrop_path":"/hiqB5fFZ230MeFAGLPahoy06UOE.jpg","original_title":"For Sama","original_language":"en"},{"id":38700,"adult":false,"title":"Bad Boys for Life","video":false,"overview":"Marcus and Mike are forced to confront new threats, career changes, and midlife crises as they join the newly created elite team AMMO of the Miami police department to take down the ruthless Armando Armas, the vicious leader of a Miami drug cartel.","genre_ids":[53,28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.8324,"vote_count":8632,"poster_path":"/y95lQLnuNKdPAzw9F9Ab8kJ80c3.jpg","release_date":"2020-01-15","vote_average":7.121,"backdrop_path":"/eAIHqfS3kXm7kZl4j7ZBfdegyEz.jpg","original_title":"Bad Boys for Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":339984,"adult":false,"title":"Miracles from Heaven","video"