st and hired ship crew to travel to mysterious Skull Island, where they encounter Kong, a giant ape who is immediately smitten with the leading lady.","genre_ids":[12,18,28],"popularity":7.8944,"vote_count":8357,"poster_path":"/6a2HY6UmD7XiDD3NokgaBAXEsD2.jpg","release_date":"2005-12-12","vote_average":6.887,"backdrop_path":"/mRM2NB0i3wv4HqxXvwIjEVi4Qqq.jpg","original_title":"King Kong","original_language":"en"},{"id":255,"adult":false,"title":"Stolen Kisses","video":false,"overview":"The third in a series of films featuring François Truffaut's alter-ego, Antoine Doinel, the story resumes with Antoine being discharged from military service. His sweetheart Christine's father lands Antoine a job as a security guard, which he promptly loses. Stumbling into a position assisting a private detective, Antoine falls for his employers' seductive wife, Fabienne, and finds that he must choose between the older woman and Christine.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":3.2789,"vote_count":455,"poster_path":"/5qHh1Vp2TOOX5IaTVt4wyT8OTnR.jpg","release_date":"1968-09-04","vote_average":7.287,"backdrop_path":"/fPFuTcXcxYR6odkHA7PW786ZWjV.jpg","original_title":"Baisers volés","original_language":"fr"},{"id":256,"adult":false,"title":"Antoine and Colette","video":false,"overview":"Now aged 17, Antoine Doinel works in a factory which makes records. At a music concert, he meets a girl his own age, Colette, and falls in love with her. Later, Antoine goes to extraordinary lengths to please his new girlfriend and her parents, but Colette still only regards him as a casual friend. First segment of “Love at Twenty” (1962).","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"popularity":0.7516,"vote_count":273,"poster_path":"/nfP8J7pv75KOAliIM3RG7h6Zos5.jpg","release_date":"1962-06-22","vote_average":7.201,"backdrop_path":"/ymtwNtiuZwbYa1Vetp68VOGgrw3.jpg","original_title":"Antoine et Colette","original_language":"fr"},{"id":421,"adult":false,"title":"The Life Aquatic with Steve Zissou","video":false,"overview":"Renowned oceanographer Steve Zissou has sworn vengeance upon the rare shark that devoured a member of his crew. In addition to his regular team, he is joined on his boat by Ned, a man who believes Zissou to be his father, and Jane, a journalist pregnant by a married man. They travel the sea, all too often running into pirates and, perhaps more traumatically, various figures from Zissou's past, including his estranged wife, Eleanor.","genre_ids":[12,35,18],"popularity":2.1726,"vote_count":3099,"poster_path":"/qZoFLNBC78jzboWeDH6Ha0qavF2.jpg","release_date":"2004-12-10","vote_average":7.078,"backdrop_path":"/7tWktnLQ81G8pHUkhuTebcTkcB3.jpg","original_title":"The Life Aquatic with Steve Zissou","original_language":"en"},{"id":271561,"adult":false,"title":"The Blue Angel","video":false,"overview":"Remake of Josef von Sternberg's 1930 classic.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3732,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/9NnL1fYA8f4VuPrKoNgXZ6dOxoP.jpg","release_date":"1959-09-04","vote_average":5.1,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The Blue Angel","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt10431500","twitter_id":"kogustakimucize","facebook_id":"yedincikogustakimucize","wikidata_id":"Q73804850","instagram_id":"7.kogustakimucizefilm","mydramalist_id":"331873","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/miracle_in_cell_no_7_2020"},"social_ids":{"twitter":"kogustakimucize","facebook":"yedincikogustakimucize","instagram":"7.kogustakimucizefilm"},"gdvg_id":110557,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2019-10-10T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CL","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2020-03-13T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":